The paper proposes a new approach for node embedding using linear models, which is a common topic in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The proposed method is evaluated on tasks such as link prediction and node clustering, which are related to social networks and information retrieval (cs.SI). The paper also mentions the use of graph convolutional networks (GCN), which are commonly used in neural networks (cs.NE) and computer vision (cs.CV) applications.
